>
<Fragment slot="head">
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="uk" href="https://www.fulfillmentmtp.com.ua/ua/fulfilment-kyiv/">
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="ru" href="https://www.fulfillmentmtp.com.ua/ru/fulfilment-kiev/">
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en" href="https://www.fulfillmentmtp.com.ua/en/fulfillment-kyiv/">
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="x-default" href="https://www.fulfillmentmtp.com.ua/ua/fulfilment-kyiv/">
</Fragment>

<!-- HERO — clean, statement-driven -->
<section class="ek-hero">
<div class="ek-hero-inner">
<div class="badge">KYIV, UKRAINE</div>
<h1>Your logistics base<br>in Eastern Europe.</h1>
<p class="ek-sub">3,700 m&sup2; warehouse near Kyiv. Ship your products to us &mdash; we store, pack, and deliver to 37M+ Ukrainian consumers. No local team. No local entity. English-speaking support.</p>
<form class="hero-form" id="heroForm"><input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="Phone or WhatsApp" maxlength="25" required autocomplete="tel" aria-label="Phone"><button type="submit">Get started &#8594;</button></form>
<div class="ek-trust">Sellers from Turkey &middot; EU &middot; UK &middot; US already onboard</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT YOU NEED — onboarding checklist, unique to EN -->
<section class="ek-checklist"><div class="ctr">
<h2 class="sec-h2">What you need to start selling in Ukraine</h2>
<div class="ek-cl-grid">
<div class="ek-cl-card ek-cl-yes">
<div class="ek-cl-icon">&#10003;</div>
<h3>Products to ship</h3>
<p>Send via DHL, FedEx, UPS, or freight to our warehouse near Boryspil Airport. We handle customs-cleared goods.</p>
</div>
<div class="ek-cl-card ek-cl-yes">
<div class="ek-cl-icon">&#10003;</div>
<h3>15 minutes for a call</h3>
<p>We discuss your products, volumes, and target marketplaces. Free consultation, no commitment.</p>
</div>
<div class="ek-cl-card ek-cl-yes">
<div class="ek-cl-icon">&#10003;</div>
<h3>Digital signature</h3>
<p>Contract signed electronically. No travel to Ukraine needed. We set up everything remotely.</p>
</div>
<div class="ek-cl-card ek-cl-no">
<div class="ek-cl-icon">&#10007;</div>
<h3>Ukrainian entity</h3>
<p>Not needed to start. We process shipments for your test launch. Register later when volumes justify it.</p>
</div>
<div class="ek-cl-card ek-cl-no">
<div class="ek-cl-icon">&#10007;</div>
<h3>Local staff</h3>
<p>Our team of 30+ handles everything. English-speaking account manager assigned to you.</p>
</div>
<div class="ek-cl-card ek-cl-no">
<div class="ek-cl-icon">&#10007;</div>
<h3>Warehouse knowledge</h3>
<p>We manage WMS, inventory, packing, labeling, shipping. You see results in your dashboard.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div></section>

<!-- VIDEO TOUR — warehouse walkthrough -->
<section class="ek-tour"><div class="ctr">
<div class="ek-tour-grid">
<div class="ek-tour-text">
<div class="badge">FACILITY</div>
<h2>See our Kyiv warehouse</h2>
<p>Two locations in Kyiv Oblast. 15 minutes from Boryspil International Airport. Direct access to M-06/E40 highway connecting to EU via Poland.</p>
<div class="ek-wh-cards">
<div class="ek-wh"><strong>Shchaslive</strong><span>2,700 m&sup2; &middot; Main hub</span></div>
<div class="ek-wh"><strong>Bilohorodka</strong><span>1,000 m&sup2; &middot; FEFO zone</span></div>
</div>
<ul class="ek-facts">
<li><strong>3 diesel generators</strong> &mdash; zero downtime since 2022</li>
<li><strong>2 fiber ISPs + Starlink</strong> &mdash; always connected</li>
<li><strong>4 Nova Poshta pickups/day</strong> &mdash; same-day dispatch</li>
<li><strong>30-second order assembly</strong> &mdash; WMS-driven</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ek-tour-video">
<div class="ek-vthumb" onclick="openVideoModal('bHY3cFF9SlI')" style="cursor:pointer">
<img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/bHY3cFF9SlI/maxresdefault.jpg" onerror="this.src='https://img.youtube.com/vi/bHY3cFF9SlI/hqdefault.jpg'" alt="MTP Group warehouse tour" width="640" height="360" loading="lazy">
<div class="ek-play">&#9654;</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div></section>

<!-- COMPLIANCE — taxes, entity, customs — unique to EN -->
<section class="ek-compliance"><div class="ctr">
<div class="badge badge-dark">COMPLIANCE</div>
<h2 class="sec-h2">The legal side, simplified</h2>
<div class="ek-comp-grid">
<div class="ek-comp-card">
<h3>Phase 1: Test launch</h3>
<div class="ek-phase">No entity</div>
<p>Ship products to our warehouse. We process orders under our entity. You validate market demand with zero paperwork. Duration: as long as you need.</p>
</div>
<div class="ek-comp-card">
<h3>Phase 2: Growth</h3>
<div class="ek-phase">FOP registration</div>
<p>When you hit 50+ orders/day, register a Ukrainian FOP (sole proprietor). Our legal partners handle it in 2-3 weeks. Simplified tax: 5% of revenue.</p>
</div>
<div class="ek-comp-card">
<h3>Phase 3: Scale</h3>
<div class="ek-phase">LLC (optional)</div>
<p>For larger operations, a Ukrainian LLC gives more flexibility. VAT registration, multiple employees, broader banking access. We connect you with accountants.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p class="ek-comp-note">Customs: we accept customs-cleared goods only. Ship via DHL/FedEx with commercial invoice &mdash; they handle clearance at Boryspil.</p>
</div></section>

<!-- COST — interactive calculator -->
<section class="ek-calc"><div class="ctr">
<div class="badge badge-dark">CALCULATOR</div>
<h2 class="sec-h2">Estimate your monthly cost</h2>
<div class="ek-calc-wrap">
<div class="ek-calc-inputs">
<label>Orders per day<input type="range" id="ekOrders" min="5" max="500" value="50" step="5"><div class="ek-cv"><span id="ekOrdVal">50</span> orders/day</div></label>
<label>Storage volume<input type="range" id="ekVolume" min="1" max="50" value="5" step="1"><div class="ek-cv"><span id="ekVolVal">5</span> m&sup3;</div></label>
</div>
<div class="ek-calc-result">
<div class="ek-calc-uah"><span id="ekTotal">27,550</span> <small>UAH/mo</small></div>
<div class="ek-calc-usd">&asymp; $<span id="ekUsd">626</span>/mo</div>
<div class="ek-calc-detail" id="ekDetail">Fulfillment: 24,200 + Storage: 3,350</div>
<div class="ek-calc-inc">Includes: WMS, packing, labels, Nova Poshta</div>
</div>
</div>
</div></section>

<!-- PRICING TABLE -->
<section class="ek-pricing"><div class="ctr">
<div class="badge badge-dark">PRICING 2026</div>
<h2 class="sec-h2">Transparent pricing. No hidden fees.</h2>
<div class="ek-price-tbl">
<div class="ek-pr ek-pr-h"><span>Service</span><span>Condition</span><span>UAH</span><span>USD</span></div>
<div class="ek-pr"><span>Fulfillment</span><span>200+ orders/day</span><span>18</span><span>$0.41</span></div>
<div class="ek-pr"><span>Fulfillment</span><span>100-199/day</span><span>20</span><span>$0.45</span></div>
<div class="ek-pr"><span>Fulfillment</span><span>50-99/day</span><span>22</span><span>$0.50</span></div>
<div class="ek-pr"><span>Fulfillment</span><span>0-49/day</span><span>26</span><span>$0.59</span></div>
<div class="ek-pr"><span>Storage</span><span>per m&sup3;/mo</span><span>650</span><span>$14.77</span></div>
<div class="ek-pr"><span>Receiving</span><span>per unit</span><span>3</span><span>$0.07</span></div>
<div class="ek-pr ek-pr-hl"><span>Monthly min</span><span></span><span>5,000</span><span>$114</span></div>
</div>
<p class="ek-pr-note">Rate: 1 USD &asymp; 44 UAH. All-inclusive: WMS, materials, Nova Poshta shipping.</p>
</div></section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="ek-faq"><div class="ctr">
<div class="badge">FAQ</div>
<h2 class="sec-h2">Questions international sellers ask</h2>
<div class="ek-faq-list">
<div class="ek-faq-item"><button class="ek-faq-q">Why is Kyiv Oblast the best location for a fulfillment warehouse in Ukraine?</button><div class="ek-faq-a"><p>Kyiv Oblast holds 30-40% of Ukraine's total warehouse capacity and sits at the intersection of major highways (M-06/E40 to the EU via Poland) and Boryspil International Airport. An order shipped from Kyiv reaches any Ukrainian buyer within 1-2 days, and the 3.5 million consumers in Kyiv metro get next-day delivery.</p></div></div>
<div class="ek-faq-item"><button class="ek-faq-q">How close is your warehouse to Boryspil Airport?</button><div class="ek-faq-a"><p>Our main warehouse in Shchaslive is 15 minutes from Boryspil International Airport. International shipments via DHL, FedEx, or UPS arrive and are processed the same day. The second warehouse in Bilohorodka has direct access to the Zhytomyr highway connecting to the EU via Poland.</p></div></div>
<div class="ek-faq-item"><button class="ek-faq-q">Can you ship from Kyiv to EU countries?</button><div class="ek-faq-a"><p>Yes. While our primary coverage is domestic Ukraine via Nova Poshta, we also ship internationally via UPS, DHL, and Meest. Cross-border shipping to Poland typically takes 2-3 business days. Ukraine's DCFTA with the EU simplifies trade documentation.</p></div></div>
<div class="ek-faq-item"><button class="ek-faq-q">What legal steps does a foreign company need to sell in Ukraine from your Kyiv warehouse?</button><div class="ek-faq-a"><p>Phase 1 (test launch): no entity needed &mdash; we process orders under our company. Phase 2 (growth): register a Ukrainian FOP (sole proprietor) in 2-3 weeks, simplified 5% tax. Phase 3 (scale): optional LLC for broader banking and VAT registration. Our legal partners handle all paperwork.</p></div></div>
<div class="ek-faq-item"><button class="ek-faq-q">What time zone does your Kyiv warehouse operate in?</button><div class="ek-faq-a"><p>UTC+2 (EET) / UTC+3 (EEST during summer). Warehouse operates 08:00-20:00 daily, including weekends. Order cutoff for same-day dispatch is 14:00 Kyiv time. We overlap with European business hours and are accessible in the morning for US East Coast clients.</p></div></div>
<div class="ek-faq-item"><button class="ek-faq-q">How fast is Kyiv-to-Kyiv delivery for local buyers?</button><div class="ek-faq-a"><p>Same-day or next-morning delivery within the Kyiv metropolitan area via Nova Poshta Express. Standard Nova Poshta delivers next-day to all Kyiv addresses. For 3.5 million consumers in the capital region, this is the fastest fulfillment speed available in Ukraine.</p></div></div>
<div class="ek-faq-item"><button class="ek-faq-q">Is the Kyiv area safe for storing commercial inventory?</button><div class="ek-faq-a"><p>Kyiv Oblast has been operationally stable since mid-2022. Our warehouses operate with 24/7 security, CCTV, insured inventory, and triple-redundant infrastructure (generators, Starlink, dual ISPs). We have maintained zero inventory losses and zero operational downtime days since February 2022.</p></div></div>
</div>
</div></section>

<!-- SEO ARTICLE -->
<section class="ek-article">
<div class="ctr">
<div class="badge badge-dark">GUIDE</div>
<h2>Kyiv as a logistics gateway: transport corridors, airport proximity, and delivery speed</h2>
<div class="ek-article-body">
<h3>The transport corridor advantage</h3>
<p>Kyiv sits at the convergence of Ukraine's most critical logistics arteries. The M-06/E40 highway connects directly to Poland and the EU single market. The M-01 runs north toward Belarus and the Baltic states. The M-05 leads south to Odesa, Ukraine's primary port. Railway junctions in the Kyiv region handle over 40% of the country's freight traffic. For a fulfillment warehouse, this means unmatched connectivity: domestic shipments reach any destination in Ukraine within 1-2 days, and cross-border shipments to Poland arrive in 48-72 hours.</p>

<h3>Boryspil Airport: receiving international inventory</h3>
<p>MTP Group's main warehouse is 15 minutes from Boryspil International Airport, Ukraine's largest cargo hub. International sellers ship inventory via DHL, FedEx, UPS, or freight forwarder, and goods arrive at the warehouse the same day they clear customs. For European suppliers, road freight from Poland to our Kyiv warehouse takes approximately 24 hours. This proximity eliminates the multi-day transit delays that plague remote warehouse locations and allows for rapid inventory replenishment.</p>

<h3>Kyiv metro: next-morning delivery for 3.5 million consumers</h3>
<p>The Kyiv metropolitan area is home to 3.5 million consumers &mdash; the highest-purchasing-power demographic in Ukraine. Orders fulfilled from a Kyiv-area warehouse reach these buyers via Nova Poshta Express within hours, enabling same-day or next-morning delivery. No other Ukrainian city offers this combination of population density and delivery speed. For international brands launching in Ukraine, Kyiv buyers generate disproportionately high conversion rates due to faster delivery expectations being met consistently.</p>

<h3>Time zone alignment with European markets</h3>
<p>Kyiv operates in the EET/EEST time zone (UTC+2 / UTC+3 summer), which overlaps significantly with European business hours. London is 2 hours behind, Berlin 1 hour behind, and Istanbul is in the same time zone. For US East Coast clients, morning communication windows exist from 09:00-12:00 EST. This alignment means your English-speaking account manager at MTP Group is available during your working day for real-time updates, issue resolution, and strategic discussions.</p>

<h3>Comparative analysis: Kyiv vs Lviv vs Odesa for fulfillment</h3>
<p>While Lviv offers EU proximity and Odesa provides port access, neither matches Kyiv for e-commerce fulfillment. Kyiv's central location ensures the fastest average delivery time to all Ukrainian regions. The capital has the deepest labor pool for warehouse operations. Boryspil Airport provides the best international cargo connectivity. And Kyiv Oblast's warehouse market is the most developed, with modern facilities equipped with power backup and automation infrastructure that smaller regional centers lack.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>

